pid":"8e81fb72426762020cdd066e4de3c3f00a767161","tid":286973,"uid":37525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T08:41:37.000Z","msg":"搵到篇咁嘢<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n香港傳媒讀錯音的現象普遍，除了當事人讀書不求甚解，態度輕率，以及有關機構主事人輕視中文，沒有監管，還因為某些「正音」人士的錯音和限音。其中多音字限定只讀一音者最多，我將繼續以教育局出版的《香港小學學習字詞表》為反面教材。<br />\n<br />\n刺，字詞表粵語標讀次，詞例有刺激、刺繡。其實，刺字常讀作「食8」（中入聲），行刺、遇刺都讀這個音。現時香港傳媒不少將行刺誤讀「行次」或誤寫「行弒」；遇刺誤讀「遇次」或誤寫「遇弒」。字詞表編者宜記取教訓，有所補充。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cantoneseculture.com/page_MediaNewsJournal/journal20080307_001.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cantoneseculture.com%2Fpage_MediaNewsJournal%2Fjournal20080307_001.aspx&d=UTsygWYPle7kxShlRc9867IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=62881e90\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cantoneseculture.com/page_MediaNewsJournal/journal20080307_001.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n行弒/遇弒係誤寫<br />\n都唔知邊撚個戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a60c06cb7f45a381fe6c1a3242e4f7c4addaa3","tid":286973,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽過新聞講過好多次遇食喎巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n的確"},{"pid":"81ee46d22aa8d50cea6b2a9905eb945f465b1a81","tid":286973,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽過新聞講過好多次遇食喎巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n的確</blockquote><br />\n古裝片好多都讀食"},{"pid":"bf9522d0011ec52c35a72e5850fc12d3bf3a77f1","tid":286973,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係有人讀 食架<br />\n不過好兩個字黎</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/肯尼迪遇刺案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%82%AF%E5%B0%BC%E8%BF%AA%E9%81%87%E5%88%BA%E6%A1%88&d=UTsygWYPle7kxShlRc9867IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8f14b648\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/肯尼迪遇刺案</a><br />\n我聽親人讀都係甘迺迪遇食案。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n200% <br />\n岩岩tvb互動新聞台 都係 讀遇「食」<br />\n講緊 美國有個議員 打棒球比人槍擊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/144546_6f2bebd2967b7f88e9d774e4ddb39fb5.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F144546_6f2bebd2967b7f88e9d774e4ddb39fb5.jpg&d=UTsygWYPle7kxShlRc9867IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e373f042\" target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/144546_6f2bebd2967b7f88e9d774e4ddb39fb5.jpg</a>&quot;  /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n異讀字<br />\n<br />\n話唔可以讀食個堆人可以收嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係異讀係 &quot;錫&quot;<br />\n&quot;食&quot;究竟係聽錯定讀錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇清楚個音節先啦"},{"pid":"c6425d4449c313ce33fc139623d25aacbf36d71e","tid":286973,"uid":81187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:24:48.000Z","msg":"食 (sik6) 係粵拼第六聲，傳統陽入聲。<br />\n「遇刺」、「行刺」同 ci3 次 唔同嘅讀音係 sik3，粵拼第三聲，傳統中入聲。<br />\n都唔同音。<br />\n<br />\n即是「遇刺」、「行刺」讀音當唱出嚟，應該會係「mi fa」、「do fa」；數字讀音音階就係好似你講「二四」、「零四」咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果讀「遇食」、「行食」，就好似唱「mi mi」、「do mi」咁（或讀數字「二二」、「零二」）。"},{"pid":"63ebdfaaf199eb96387bc3b4e946106d8511e140","tid":286973,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"你係大陸人講胡語？"},{"pid":"97be1e5b27be53db924af2b7d3baeeaea374207f","tid":286973,"uid":50351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係有人讀 食架<br />\n不過好兩個字黎</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/肯尼迪遇刺案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%82%AF%E5%B0%BC%E8%BF%AA%E9%81%87%E5%88%BA%E6%A1%88&d=UTsygWYPle7kxShlRc9867IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8f14b648\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/肯尼迪遇刺案</a><br />\n我聽親人讀都係甘迺迪遇食案。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n200% <br />\n岩岩tvb互動新聞台 都係 讀遇「食」<br />\n講緊 美國有個議員 打棒球比人槍擊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/144546_6f2bebd2967b7f88e9d774e4ddb39fb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F144546_6f2bebd2967b7f88e9d774e4ddb39fb5.jpg&h=04dcc28e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n異讀字<br />\n<br />\n話唔可以讀食個堆人可以收嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你click 入去聽下佢點讀先再叫人收嗲啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25同36聲不嬲難分架啦，你估個個都音感好？要唔要睇下大學中文系死傷最慘既係邊科，咪就係聲韻學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加埋有配詞就容易有變調誤讀，話佢可以讀食係唔準確，但確實係有近似讀音，話聽都無聽過就係大錯特錯，點解唔可以叫佢地收嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a526d2c83e7670a7fb96e2ddb3fc3e73df36a2f9","tid":286973,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T18:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係有人讀 食架<br />\n不過好兩個字黎</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/肯尼迪遇刺案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%82%AF%E5%B0%BC%E8%BF%AA%E9%81%87%E5%88%BA%E6%A1%88&d=UTsygWYPle7kxShlRc9867IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8f14b648\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/肯尼迪遇刺案</a><br />\n我聽親人讀都係甘迺迪遇食案。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n200% <br />\n岩岩tvb互動新聞台 都係 讀遇「食」<br />\n講緊 美國有個議員 打棒球比人槍擊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/144546_6f2bebd2967b7f88e9d774e4ddb39fb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F144546_6f2bebd2967b7f88e9d774e4ddb39fb5.jpg&h=04dcc28e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n異讀字<br />\n<br />\n話唔可以讀食個堆人可以收嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你click 入去聽下佢點讀先再叫人收嗲啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25同36聲不嬲難分架啦，你估個個都音感好？要唔要睇下大學中文系死傷最慘既係邊科，咪就係聲韻學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加埋有配詞就容易有變調誤讀，話佢可以讀食係唔準確，但確實係有近似讀音，話聽都無聽過就係大錯特錯，點解唔可以叫佢地收嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n向中大條link到<br />\n我聽完真係分唔到同個食字有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好明顯係聽得出同個食字個音有少少唔同<br />\n但我又講唔出個分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3b2d67efe761686bb7d6ed8efaa6928355390a","tid":286973,"uid":50351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/肯尼迪遇刺案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%82%AF%E5%B0%BC%E8%BF%AA%E9%81%87%E5%88%BA%E6%A1%88&d=UTsygWYPle7kxShlRc9867IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8f14b648\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/肯尼迪遇刺案</a><br />\n我聽親人讀都係甘迺迪遇食案。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n200% <br />\n岩岩tvb互動新聞台 都係 讀遇「食」<br />\n講緊 美國有個議員 打棒球比人槍擊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/144546_6f2bebd2967b7f88e9d774e4ddb39fb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F144546_6f2bebd2967b7f88e9d774e4ddb39fb5.jpg&h=04dcc28e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n異讀字<br />\n<br />\n話唔可以讀食個堆人可以收嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你click 入去聽下佢點讀先再叫人收嗲啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25同36聲不嬲難分架啦，你估個個都音感好？要唔要睇下大學中文系死傷最慘既係邊科，咪就係聲韻學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加埋有配詞就容易有變調誤讀，話佢可以讀食係唔準確，但確實係有近似讀音，話聽都無聽過就係大錯特錯，點解唔可以叫佢地收嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n向中大條link到<br />\n我聽完真係分唔到同個食字有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好明顯係聽得出同個食字個音有少少唔同<br />\n但我又講唔出個分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係粵語9聲點解會玩死非母語既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係因為仄聲詞既25同36聲好撚難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多人都係靠狂讀精/靈個類辨分法試聲調加鳩估先拎到個pass咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算母語既人都難分上同去聲啦，語言學，IPA，聲韻，講音準既野真係睇天份架，分到就分到，分唔到你點講，講埋發音器官，講埋發音速度對方都唔會明。字既讀音相同，唔同既係個調，但未聽過個讀音就係衝出黎柒囉<br />\n<br />\n利申 分唔到上去聲 入聲靠明個尾音唔可以長發先分到，好明白分唔到搞到讀得唔準確既係咩思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本修正唔到"}]}